{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1694-12_146","@resp":"wordpro","head":{"value":"[Cantique sur les vaines occupations des gens du Siecle, tiré de divers endroits d’Isaïe &amp; de Jeremie]","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", décembre 1694 [tome 12], p. 146-151.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"Je reserve pour le mois prochain la suite de cette Relation, afin de diversifier les matieres, &amp; ne doute point que les Vers que vous allez lire ne vous fassent le mesme plaisir qu’ils ont fait à tout ce qu’il y a de bons Connoisseurs. Leur tour aisé vous fera connoistre qu’ils partent de source, &amp; que l’Auteur a tous les talens qui peuvent faire réussir avec avantage, quand on entreprend un ouvrage de Poësie. La matiere en est relevée, &amp; il seroit difficile de la traiter avec plus de force, ny plus noblement.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"#1":{"value":"CANTIQUE","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#1"},"lb":{},"#2":{"value":"Sur les vaines occupations des gens du Siecle, tiré de divers endroits d’Isaïe &amp; de Jeremie.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#2"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quel charme vainqueur du monde","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vers Dieu m’éleve aujourd’huy ?","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Malheureux l’homme qui fonde","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sur les hommes son appuy !","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Leur gloire fuit &amp; s’efface","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En moins de temps que la trace","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Du Vaisseau qui fend les mers,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ou de la fléche rapide,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui loin de l’œil qui la guide","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Cherche l’oiseau dans les airs.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" De la Sagesse immortelle","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La voix touche &amp; nous instruit.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Enfans des hommes, dit-elle,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De vos soins quel est le fruit ?","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Par quelle erreur, Ames vaines,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Du plus pur sang de vos veines","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Achetez vous si souvent,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Non un pain qui vous repaisse,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais une ombre qui vous laisse","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Plus affamez que devant.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[19]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Le Pain que je vous propose","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sert aux Anges d’aliment.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dieu luy-mesme le compose","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De la fleur de son froment.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est ce Pain si delectable","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que ne sert point à sa table","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le monde que vous suivez.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je l’offre à qui me veut suivre,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Approchez ; voulez-vous vivre ?","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Venez, mangez, &amp; vivez.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" O Sagesse, ta parole","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Fit éclorre l’Univers,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Posa sur un double Pole","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La Terre au milieu des Mers.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tu dis, &amp; les Cieux parurent,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et tous les Astres coururent","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans leur ordre se placer.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Avant les Siecles tu regnes,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et qui suis-je que tu daignes","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Jusqu’à moy te rabaisser ?","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[19]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Le Verbe, Image du Pere,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Laissa son Trône éternel,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et d’une mortelle Mere","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Voulut naistre homme &amp; mortel.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Comme l’orgueil fut le crime,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont il naissoit la victime,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il dépoüilla sa splendeur,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et vint, pauvre &amp; miserable,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Apprendre à l’homme coupable","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sa veritable grandeur.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" L’ame heureusement captive","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sous ton joug trouve la paix,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et s’abbreuve d’une eau vive,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui ne s’épuise jamais.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Chacun peut boire en cette onde,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle invite tout le monde,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais nous courons follement","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Chercher des sources bourbeuses","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En des Citernes trompeuses,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont l’eau fuit à tout moment.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[19]/#"}}]}}]}}}